# playground/ingest

Shared helpers: `ingest_utils.py` (tables, formulas, pictures, markdown placeholders).

## Scripts

| Script | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `docling-a1.py` | SmolVLM captions + confidence grades → `output/ingest/` |
| `docling-medical-a1.py` | Medical parse baseline (no chunking) |
| `docling_parse_pdf.py` | Lower-level PDF → pages API |
| `mineru-a1.py` | MinerU alternative backend |

## docling-a1.py caveats

- Hard-coded `papers/test_ingest/` input, `output/ingest/` output.
- Currently processes first PDF only (`break` in `main`) and `page_range=(5, 7)` — document when changing behavior.

## Docling patterns

- Set `HF_HUB_DISABLE_SYMLINKS_WARNING` and `TRANSFORMERS_VERBOSITY` before imports.
- GPU: `AcceleratorDevice.CUDA if torch.cuda.is_available() else CPU`.
- Prefetch models: `uv run docling-tools models download`.
